name: Cumulus Trucker by Queen Bee
description:
This courier-style bag is great for students, cyclists, parents and anyone who needs a little extra space for toting around all that essential.....stuff.  Handmade of high-quality waterproof vinyl, has two front pockets underneath flap, an additional layer of vinyl on bottom of bag for reinforcement, adjustable heavy duty seat belt webbing strap, and a silver velvet lined flap that closes with two snaps. All are made with black vinyl bodies.

Trucker Size: 15"w x 12" h x 4.5" d 
Strap Length: Minimum: 30" Maximum: 60"

name: Kyoto Tote by Queen Bee
description:
They brought an updated version of the Kyoto design back, due to popular demand. Tiny flowers dot the graceful branches of a cherry blossom tree. 

Lined with sturdy blue & white striped cotton canvas ticking. The inside features a pocket to keep your little bits separate and easy to find. The straps are lined with webbing for strength and to prevent stretching. Closes with two snaps at the base of the handles. Hand made of high quality vinyl in their Portland studio. 
Choose Brown, Sage, Cream, or Plum

Large $82 Brown, Sage, Cream
Size: 15" wide x 13" high x 5" deep 
Straps: 23" long
